      "side": 1,
      "message": "Just general comment, you are keeping alive both dynamic and not dynamic cases. Is there a benefit for having the not dynamic case? Is the extra code complexing, extra shaders, etc. worth it? From what I can tell the main difference is whether we are passing in the stroke info via vert attribs or uniforms.",
